document.topic_text: Symbol Key * Not all on this points score were offered places. ** Matriculated candidates are considered but admission is on the basis of performance in the music test and interview. *** Applicants are ranked as for other courses but the final decision depends on performance in interview. # Test / Interview / Portfolio etc. v New competition for Available/Vacant Places. + Includes Project / Portfolio Score. Please note The details given are for general information only and do not form part of any contract.
